casebody.data:
Michael R. HOOK, Appellant/Petitioner(s),
v.
Patsy FURNISH, f/k/a Patsy Lynn Hook, Appellee/Respondent(s). CASE NO.: 2D17-0776 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Second District. April 5, 2018

BY ORDER OF THE COURT:

Having received no response from the appellant/former husband to our March 12, 2018, order to show cause, we dismissed this appeal as moot.

KELLY, CRENSHAW, and BLACK, JJ., Concur.
